description:
Federation charm in quiet location
Combining a light-filled design with plenty of charm, this Federation-style residence offers immaculate living on more than a quarter of an acre. The quality brick veneer home is surrounded by magnificent gardens with a sun-drenched, north-facing yard and an alfresco area with café blinds providing the perfect setting for outdoor entertaining.
The single-level design showcases an inviting living room with a gas log fireplace, generous updated kitchen enhanced by an abundance of storage solutions and adjoins both meals and study/sitting room.
Other additions include:
3 bedrooms with built-in robes;
Study;
Family bathroom;
Split-system air-conditioning;
Solar roof panels & solar hot water;
Water tank;
Garage and carport with workshop;
Circular driveway perfect for a boat, caravan or trailer; and
Flat 1184m2 (approx.) block with mature trees
Nestled in a quiet enclave on a fully-fenced corner allotment, this tranquil retreat offers convenient living just steps to Dartnell Reserve and moments from shops, schools and transport.
